description: The town of Burton Latimer is located in between Kettering and Wellingborough in the county of Northamptonshire. This walk from the town takes you over the River Ise and the Midland Railway Line to visit the neighbouring village of Isham. You can extend your walk by continuing south west to visit neighbouring Orlingbury .
